snippet.title: Hell Inspector's Mod of Stupidity (Reveal Trailer) - The Simpsons Hit And Run Mod
snippet.description:
This is it, finally a trailer for this thing.

This Simpsons Hit & Run Mod combines the worlds of The Simpsons, Wallace & Gromit, King of the Hill, South Park and many others to bring together this decently sized crossover mod.

Do things go well? Most likely.

Complete with New Characters, Unlockable Cars, New Missions, Map Additions and A Bunch More.

For more news on the mod
https://forum.donutteam.com/forum/topic/3112
